{
  "stem": "1387.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after my father's death, I also had to support-- help support my family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At the time, I was doing a specialty work, which was painting labels on pharmaceutical bottles and jars.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The law required in Poland in those years-- in 1937, 1938-- that every pharmacy has permanent labels on their, on their medical jars.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, and, and I was the only one that was recommended to do this kind of work.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Otherwise, they had to send those jars to the factory in Czechoslovakia or in Austria, where they were originally purchased.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I was going from one pharmacy to another, throughout Galicia-- former Galicia in, in the part of Poland.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was doing that for several years and helping out my family and earning a living.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the best to my recollection is that students in Lemberg and Lwow were beaten up and cut up with razor blades when they went to school.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was one of the reasons my father felt that's not a good place to study in, that the best thing to do is to go get ready to go to Palestine where a Jew would be considered equal.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was mostly by the index-- the index?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Poland, generally, is anti-Semitic country.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from my experience, if it wouldn't have been for the Poles or the Ukrainians, a lot of Jews would have been saved during the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, it was worse.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, it wasn't very good during Pilsudski's times.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then later on, it was worst.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was open anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I never received it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in 1939, the war broke out between the-- the, the Germans attacked Poland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a agreement between the Soviet Union and the German government.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
